<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Index Up Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 4 (Xinhua) -- The index of Tehran Stock Exchange
closed at 1604.45 points on Saturday, up 0.10 points from that on
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The stock market did not open on Thursday and Friday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 3.46 million shares changed hands with a turnover of
13.45 billion rials (about 2.45 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 12 companies made gains while those of 17 others
declined. 
</P>
