said that, as a former prisoner, he knew that there could never be
a chance for freed prisoners or inmates to be present at
executions. Because of this, he said, it would be impossible for
the man to be an eyewitness as he testified.
</P>
<P>
The official pointed out that it was not accidental for some
people in the U.S. House of Representatives to "stage the farce."
Some forces hostile to China in the Untied States do not want to
see China grow strong, and do not want to see the healthy
development of China-US relations, he said.  
</P>
</TEXT>
